name: Space Delivery (Bryn, masbokus, jpanboi64)
description:
You have ordered something online, sadly it needs to be delivered from the OTHER SIDE OF THE GALAXY! Your job is to deliver the package by using the gravity-bend of black holes and avoiding asteroids on the way. Can you deliver all 11 packages in one go? :)

The controls are easy: There is one button. The mouse button. Enjoy! And let us know what you think.

Note: Please play in fullscreen for the best playing experience!

Credits:
Programming: Bryn McKerracher
Piano and Synthesizers: Mas Bokus
8-Bit Pencils: jpanboi64
